import { AppBar, Box, Toolbar, Typography, IconButton, Text } from '@mui/material'
import FacebookIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Facebook';
import './NavBar.css'



export default function NavBar() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <AppBar position="static" sx={{ bgcolor: "#255e2d" }}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography
            variant="h6"
            noWrap
            component="div"
            sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', sm: 'block' } }}
          >
            <Text>David's Gardening Services</Text>
          </Typography>
          <Typography>
            Tel: 077########
            <IconButton size="large" color="inherit">
              <FacebookIcon />
            </IconButton>
          </Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </Box >
  )
}
